{"tid":694690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(親俄親中) 特朗普：G7應該邀請「俄羅斯」重新加入","createTime":"2018-06-08T14:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T15:17:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44ef76e1655d6881ba67a3d9633820b869615dbe","tid":694690,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2091109/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2091109%2F&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fc8920c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2091109/</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普：G7應該邀請俄羅斯重新加入<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普起程前往加拿大，出席七國集團（G7）峰會。臨行前，他表示G7應該邀請俄羅斯重新加入，即回復之前的G8。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普離開華盛頓前表示，不論喜歡與否，亦可能政治不正確，但世界需要運轉，而G7卻把俄羅斯踢走，G7應該讓俄羅斯回來，因為他們需要俄羅斯現身談判桌。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯因為入侵烏克蘭克里米亞，於2014年被逐出G8，令集團變成了現時的G7。"},{"pid":"74080cefdfbea68658dc445caadf3d1c112ef3c1","tid":694690,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"岩呀，最好連同俄羅斯一齊分晒成個歐洲"},{"pid":"b8ea07ee887365af9b210a70dc5756e11b7f0008","tid":694690,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74080cefdfbea68658dc445caadf3d1c112ef3c1","tid":694690,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"岩呀，最好連同俄羅斯一齊分晒成個歐洲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"同俄羅斯跟中共分晒成個世界最好<br />\n<br />\n好過益果D包容同性戀黑人新移民既左膠政客?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2d6974f989b91da31861a0161a14cb008189f0","tid":694690,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"Trump trump 應該唔想做第二屆，用總統身份收支俄好處就算"},{"pid":"892a7b59173acf5115a5fb9d25ffc9ba5d5aad87","tid":694690,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i